metadata.description:
"Vessel Of Love" Describes the complexity of Human emotion as well as the importance of love within oneself .

Title: "Vessel Of Love" Artist: Bleu Pablo Medium: Digital Art Year: 2022

1st Collector will also receive a high quality Physical Print sent to you directly. Reach out to @Bleupablo on IG or Twitter.
